      <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-1">What Homeowners Experience</h2>
      <p className="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">Representative experiences from homeowners who used our dispatch network. Individual results may vary.</p>
      <div className="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
